article:
The following is a current 'list of [[Roman Catholic]] [[archdiocese]]s' ordered
by country and continent.

Many smaller countries, and those with small Roman Catholic populations, lack
large umbrella archdioceses and have immediately subject vicariates, dioceses,
ordinariates, apostolic exarchates, prelatures, apostolic administrations, and
prefectures (all of which may also exist in countries with one or more
archdioceses).
